title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Boeing 767-300ER - version 0.2
description:
In this video we will have a look at a the Boeing 767-300ER which has recently received a new update. The developer spend quiet some time on designing the cockpit to make sure it mimics a real 767-300. There is still some work to do but several instruments including the autopilot are already working.

If you also want to give this airport a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/26107/native-767-300er-wip
